{"tid":2231541,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］白宮發言人Kayleigh McEnany確診新型肺炎！","createTime":"2020-10-05T17:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T00:11:12.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6a06275faaca8d7e63c518e95f2727037a3ff0f5","tid":2231541,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.ktsf.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Kayleigh-McEnany-S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ktsf.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FKayleigh-McEnany-S.jpg&h=44c2b3a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白宮發言人Kayleigh McEnany周一透露她確診新型肺炎，目前已自我隔離。<br />\n<br />\nMcEnany在聲明中表示，她是周一早上確診，目前並沒有病徵，她周日傍晚曾短暫與記者談話，但她說獲准到白宮採訪的新聞工作者，當中沒有人曾與她有長時間接觸，足以被視為密切接觸者。<br />\n<br />\nMcEnany是在特朗普總統確診數天後確診，她說隔離期間仍然會為美國民眾遙距工作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ktsf.com/2020/10/05/mcenany-tests-positive-for-covid-19/?fbclid=IwAR25yV7ipA7BJAGK3V_TWIsKfjgbFhqEbM-G69IYoWPXa7Pyg_YbUR_GQoI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ktsf.com%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2Fmcenany-tests-positive-for-covid-19%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR25yV7ipA7BJAGK3V_TWIsKfjgbFhqEbM-G69IYoWPXa7Pyg_YbUR_GQoI&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL8emYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=f6b90842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ktsf.com/2020/10/05/mcenany-tests-positive-for-covid-19/?fbclid=IwAR25yV7ipA7BJAGK3V_TWIsKfjgbFhqEbM-G69IYoWPXa7Pyg_YbUR_GQoI</a>"},{"pid":"7d39638a19d0b93435455ff8b8b72145a0801f11","tid":2231541,"uid":219007,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:24:09.000Z","msg":"Sorry，我乜都未睇照copy佢個標題<br />\n<br />\n應該改返「白宮發言人Kayleigh McEnany確診<span class=\"red\">中國肺炎</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c2f9f700ab877e44c555bb9315c4c38c55cc7e","tid":2231541,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T23:12:44.000Z","msg":"我包佢出返黎更大聲屌柒支那"},{"pid":"5aa2938f